products.name: US POLO
products.product_desc: Elevate your casual wardrobe with the U.S. Polo Assn. Classic Polo Shirt. Crafted from premium  breathable cotton  this polo offers all-day comfort and durability. The classic design features a ribbed collar a three-button placket and the iconic embroidered polo player logo on the chest. Available in a variety of vibrant colors, this polo is perfect for casual outings, weekend wear, or layering under a jacket. The regular fit provides a modern yet relaxed silhouette, making it a versatile staple for any wardrobe.

products.name: ALLEN SOLLY
products.product_desc: The Allen Solly Slim Fit Formal Shirt combines elegance and sophistication with a tailored design that ensures a perfect fit. Made from high-quality, wrinkle-resistant fabric, this shirt is ideal for business meetings or formal events. It features a classic spread collar, adjustable cuffs, and a sleek button-down front. The slim fit offers a contemporary look, while the soft fabric ensures comfort throughout the day. Pair it with tailored trousers and a blazer for a polished and professional appearance.

products.name: JACK & JONES
products.product_desc: Jack & Jones Slim Fit Chinos are a stylish and versatile addition to your wardrobe. Made from a blend of soft cotton and stretch fabric, these chinos offer both comfort and mobility. The slim fit design provides a contemporary look, while the classic five-pocket styling ensures practicality. Perfect for both casual and semi-formal occasions, these chinos can be paired with a crisp shirt or a casual tee. Available in various colors, they are a must-have for any modern wardrobe.

products.name: Peter EngLand
products.product_desc: The Peter England Regular Fit Chinos offer a timeless style and unparalleled comfort. Crafted from high-quality cotton with a touch of stretch, these chinos provide a comfortable fit that moves with you. The regular fit offers a relaxed yet refined look, making these chinos suitable for a range of occasions. Featuring a button closure, belt loops, and a classic five-pocket design, these chinos are perfect for dressing up or down. Ideal for office wear or casual outings, they are a versatile addition to any wardrobe.

products.name: H&M
products.product_desc: The H&M Basic Cotton T-Shirt is a wardrobe essential that combines simplicity with comfort. Made from soft, breathable cotton, this tee is designed for everyday wear. It features a classic crew neckline, short sleeves, and a regular fit that offers a relaxed silhouette. Available in a range of colors and sizes, this versatile t-shirt can be easily paired with jeans, shorts, or layered under a jacket. Ideal for casual outings or lounging at home, it’s a staple piece that delivers both style and comfort.
